<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link href="/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-800">
    <%- include('partials/navbar', { page: '/about' }) %>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 via-red-500 to-pink-500 text-white py-16 text-center">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold">About Us</h1>
            <p class="text-lg mt-4">All about our Lego collection and passion for building</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="container mx-auto my-12 px-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
            <!-- Left column with image -->
            <div>
                <img src="https://assets.lego.com/logos/v4.5.0/brand-lego.svg" alt="About Us Image" class="rounded-lg shadow-md w-full">
            </div>

            <!-- Right column with text -->
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Who We Are</h2>
                <p class="text-lg mb-6">
                    We are a team of passionate Lego enthusiasts who have been collecting, building, and sharing our Lego sets for years. 
                    Our goal is to bring together other Lego fans and inspire creativity with our vast collection.
                </p>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">A Little About Me</h3>
                <p class="text-lg">
                    I'm Vinicius, a WEB322 student, coursing the third semester of the CPP program at Seneca College. 
                    Surviving through the last semester of the Markham Campus (R.I.P. dear campus). 
                    Besides this course, I'm also taking OOP345, DBS311, SYD366, and a course about Myths and Legends as a general knowledge requirement.
                </p>
                <p class="text-lg mt-4">
                    It's crazy to juggle all of the content with work and personal life, submitting assignments minutes before the due time, but it's worth the stress... 
                    I think...
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
